# 8. 決意

Mafuyu's Father: ...
Mafuyu's Father: (Ms. Yoisaki has been so good to Mafuyu...)
Mafuyu's Father: (On top of letting Mafuyu stay at her house, Ms. Yoisaki's been going so far to make her smile...)
Mafuyu's Father: (And Mafuyu's been willing to talk a little more recently...)
Mafuyu's Father: (It's been a slow process...)
Mafuyu's Father: (But I hope this leads to the both of them talking soon.)
Mafuyu's Father: I'm back...
Mafuyu's Father: Wait, you're...
Mafuyu's Mother: Welcome back.
Mafuyu's Father: Hello...
Mafuyu's Father: What do you have there? Are you getting some knitting done?
Mafuyu's Mother: Yes.
Mafuyu's Mother: I was just going through an album of when Mafuyu was little.
Mafuyu's Mother: It reminded me of how easily she used to catch chill...
Mafuyu's Mother: This is about all I can do for her right now.
Mafuyu's Father: I see...
Mafuyu's Father: The scarf you made looks very warm. I'm sure she's going to love it.
Mafuyu's Mother: ...
Mafuyu's Father: So, this is just an idea...
Kanade: Your dad should be arriving soon, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: Yes...
Kanade: Are you sure about this?
Mafuyu: *Nod* My mind is already made up.
Mafuyu: I'm going to see if I can talk to my mom.
Kanade: Okay...
Kanade: (Mafuyu's made up her mind...)
Kanade: (That means I also have to push forward.)
Kanade: (To learn more about her mom.)
Kanade: Oh, be right there...!
Mafuyu's Father: *Nod* You seem good again today. Any changes since we last met?
Mafuyu: No news...
Mafuyu's Father: Okay.
Mafuyu's Father: That reminds me. I have something for you, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: Huh...?
Mafuyu's Father: It's from your mother.
Mafuyu: Mom...?
Mafuyu: A scarf...?
Mafuyu's Father: Yes...
Mafuyu's Father: It can still get very cold all of a sudden, so she hopes this will help you keep warm.
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: Thank you.
Mafuyu's Father: I also have a proposal I'd like to make...
Mafuyu: What is it?
Mafuyu's Father: How would you feel about talking to your mother?
Mafuyu's Father: I feel like you've improved a considerable amount compared to before, thanks in no small part to Ms. Yoisaki's care.
Mafuyu's Father: And... Your mother is also in a condition to talk now.
Mafuyu: ...!
Mafuyu's Father: So, Mafuyu, would you be willing to try talking to her again?
Mafuyu's Father: Of course, you don't have to if you're not comfortable. And you don't have to give me your answer today.
Mafuyu's Father: Whenever you feel ready...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (With Mom...)
Mafuyu's Mother: Hehe. My, aren't we full of demands today.
Mafuyu's Mother: Of course, dear. Now, lie down for me, and take my hand...
Mafuyu's Mother: But I'm sure you'll understand, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu's Mother: Because you're such a good, kind girl who I know will do the right thing.
Mafuyu: (I'm still scared...)
Mafuyu: (But...)
Mafuyu: (I also need to start moving forward...)
Mafuyu: (Kanade's making such a sincere effort to know.)
Mafuyu: (So, I too...)
Mafuyu: Okay...
Mafuyu's Father: ...!
Mafuyu's Father: Really...?
Mafuyu: *Nod*
Mafuyu: I was also thinking I want to talk to her.
Mafuyu's Father: I see...
Mafuyu's Father: Thank you...
Mafuyu: Kanade...
Kanade: Huh?
Mafuyu: I want you there with me.
Mafuyu: When I talk to her, I want you to also be there.
Kanade: Wait, me...?
Kanade: Umm... I don't mind...
Kanade: That is, if it isn't going to be a problem...
Mafuyu's Father: Not at all. Please come join us.
Mafuyu's Father: You being there will make Mafuyu feel better.
Mafuyu's Father: You've spent all this time looking after her, so I'd greatly appreciate it if you were also present.
Kanade: Oh...
Kanade: Understood... In that case, thank you for agreeing to this.
Mafuyu: Kanade...
Kanade: It's okay...
Kanade: Let's tell her about how you really feel.
Mafuyu: *Nod*
Kanade: (This is going to be a crucial conversation for Mafuyu. So, I want to be there to support her...)
Kanade: (Also, this isn't quite how I was expecting to learn more about Mafuyu's mom, but this is going to be my chance.)
Kanade: (I have to do whatever I can.)
Kanade: (To save Mafuyu.)
